## G. Data Flow Diagrams (DFD)

### 1. Level 0 DFD (Context Diagram)
The Context Diagram provides a high-level overview of the **PauliBot** system, identifying its boundaries and the external entities that interact with it.

```mermaid
graph LR
    %% Entities
    Student["🧑 Student"]
    Guest["🧑 Guest User"]
    Admin["🧑 Administrator"]
    Gemini["🤖 Gemini API"]

    %% System
    System((0.0 PauliBot System))

    %% Flows
    Student -- "Queries / Auth Credentials" --> System
    System -- "AI Responses / History" --> Student

    Guest -- "Queries" --> System
    System -- "AI Responses" --> Guest

    Admin -- "Knowledge Base Updates / User Management" --> System
    System -- "Admin Dashboard / Status" --> Admin

    System -- "Enhanced Prompt (Context + Question)" --> Gemini
    Gemini -- "Synthetic Response" --> System
```

### 2. Level 1 DFD (Process Decomposition)
The Level 1 DFD provides a detailed decomposition of the PauliBot logic. It utilizes a **linear layout** for clarity and strictly follows the **Verb + Noun** naming convention. 

```mermaid
---
config:
  flowchart:
    curve: linear
  layout: elk
---
flowchart TD
    %% Entities
    Student["🧑 Student"]
    Guest["🧑 Guest User"]
    Admin["🧑 Administrator"]
    Gemini["🤖 Gemini API"]

    %% Data Stores
    D1[("D1: User Records")]
    D2[("D2: Chat Logs")]
    D3[("D3: Knowledge Base")]

    %% 1.0 Authentication Flow
    Student -- "Auth Credentials" --> P1(("1.0\nAuthenticate\nUser"))
    D1 -- "Verify Account" --> P1
    P1 -- "Auth Status" --> Student
    P1 -- "Authenticated Session" --> P2

    %% 2.0 Chat Processing
    Student -- "User Query" --> P2(("2.0\nProcess\nChat Query"))
    Guest -- "Guest Query" --> P2

    %% Sub-Process: RAG Search
    P2 --> P3(("3.0\nSearch\nKnowledge"))
    P3 -- "Semantic Lookup" --> D3
    D3 -- "Context Chunks" --> P3
    P3 -- "Text Context" --> P2

    %% Sub-Process: AI Generation
    P2 --> P4(("4.0\nSynthesize\nAI Response"))
    P4 -- "Structured Prompt" --> Gemini
    Gemini -- "AI String" --> P4
    P4 -- "Response Content" --> P2

    %% Sub-Process: History
    P2 --> P5(("5.0\nManage\nChat History"))
    P5 -- "Persist Message" --> D2
    D2 -- "Retrieve History" --> P5
    P5 -- "Past Conversations" --> Student

    P2 -- "Final Response" --> Student & Guest

    %% 6.0 Admin / Knowledge Management
    Admin -- "Knowledge Content" --> P6(("6.0\nUpdate\nKnowledge Base"))
    P6 -- "Store & Embed" --> D3
```
